AFDC</A>
<li><A HREF="/townhall/FRC/infocus/if95c3wl.html">Quotable Comments on 
Welfare Reform and Illegitimacy</A>
<li><A HREF="/townhall/FRC/infocus/if95c4wl.html">Family Cap Talking 
Points</A>
<li><A HREF="/townhall/FRC/infocus/if95c5wl.html">A Few Facts About 
