<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/townhall/FRC/podium/pd95k1fe.html 204.71.237.73 19970108201649 text/html 11856
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 20:16:42 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 14-Mar-96 18:48:46 GMT
