<p>

<li>Charen, Mona.  &quot;Christians Suffer Silently for the Faith.&quot;
<I>The Detroit News</I>.  December 14, 1995:  Opinion page.

<p>

<li><I>Ibid</I>.

<p>

<li>Witham, Larry.  &quot;Christians Press to End Persecution; Urge
U.S. Government to Use Its Influence.&quot;  <I>The Washington
Times.</I>  January 23, 1996:  final edition, A2.

<p>

<li>U.S. Code Service, Section 2151 (A), 1995: 22.

<p>

<li><I>Ibid.</I>

