262 (1993), pp. 2063-65.

<p>

<li>Hamer, D.H. et al. Response to Risch, N et al. <I>ibid</I>.
p. 2065.

<p>

<li>Hamer, D.H. et al. Response to Risch, N et al. <I>loc. cit.</I>

