<P><LI> "Los Angeles Times Poll Study #307 - United States Military Survey,"<I> Los Angeles Times</I>, February 1993.
<P><LI> Franklin D. Jones and Ronald J. Koshes, op. cit., P. 17.
<P><LI> Office of Assistant Secretary of Defense News Release, "Secretary Aspin Releases New Regulations on 
