Abstract of the United States 1993</I>.  U.S. Department of Commerce.
 Economics and Statistics Administration. Bureau of the Census.
1993.
<P>
<li>Ibid.
<P>
<li>&quot;Criminal Victimization in the United States, 1992,&quot;
 U.S. Department of Justice, Office of Justice Programs, Bureau
of Justice Statistics, NCJ-145125, March 1994: 31.
<P>
<li>Albert R. Roberts, &quot;Psychosocial Characteristics of Batterers:
 A Study of 234 Men Charged with Domestic Violence Offenses.&quot;
 <I>Journal of Family Violence</I>. Vol. 2, No. 1, 1987:85.
</font></ol>

<p>

